<p>You can now take crash-consistent snapshots of multiple Amazon Elastic Block Store (EBS) volumes attached to an EC2 instance with a single API call. You can also use <a href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/snapshot-lifecycle.html">Amazon Data Lifecycle Manager</a> (DLM) to automate the multi-volume snapshot management via creating lifecycle policies. <br /> </p>